posts.title: Where the duck am I???
posts.content: I think I am lost, can anybody tell me where to go??

posts.title: I've had an argument with my duck. Please recomend good psychologist..
posts.content: I am really depressed right now.. He said some things, i've done some things.. Idk how to fix it now..

posts.title: I think my rubber duck is dead.. Should I call police?
posts.content: He is not responding to me for more than an hour! I hear no heartbeat! Who could have killed him?

posts.title: What is the best rubber duck breeder in town?
posts.content: Looking for the best breeder in Vilnius. I want to participate in duck shows with my new duck friend. I will give it good home, I swear.
